
## Framework7 Rules

Documentaions CSS classes here: https://framework7.io/docs/

✅ **Use ONLY Framework7 native components:**
- Searchbar, Toolbar, Tabbar, List, Media-List, Virtual-List, Card, Button, Popup
- Framework7 Icons only

❌ **Do NOT:**
- Create custom components/navigation/buttons/modals
- Override Framework7 styles
- Use custom CSS classes for UI (only for data: `.chinese`, `.pinyin`)

## JavaScript

- ES6+ (const/let, arrow functions, async/await)
- Use `idb` library: `await openDB()`, `db.put()`, `db.get()`, `db.getAllFromIndex()`
- Framework7: `this.f7.popup.create()` for modals

## CSS

- **Only Framework7 classes** for UI components
- Only custom styles for data display (fonts, colors for specific content)